Version 2.2.2, 20 April 2017
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Fix - Problems with restricting access to variable products
* Tweak - Updated Select2 script to improve compatibility with other plugins
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

Version 2.2.1, 5 April 2017
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Feature - New option to add all new users to specific membership plan
* Fix - Shop manager unable to save plugin settings
* Fix - Expiration date is set for members who have plans with no expiration
* Fix - Full product description not displayed for products with restricted access
* Tweak - Improved compatibility with WooCommerce 3.0
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

Version 2.2, 22 June 2016
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Fix - Access restriction by URL issue
* Fix - URL restriction rules are reset on some occasions
* Fix - Issue related to creation of new WooCommerce variations
* Fix - Several issues related to CSV export tool
* Fix - Notices on WooCommerce emails page
* Tweak - All widgets are now supported by Visual Composer
* Tweak - Enabled membership plan enable/disable actions directly from plan list
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

Version 2.1, 7 February 2016
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Feature - Multiple users can now be granted access at once from Users page
* Feature - File downloads are now automatically restricted on membership expiration
* Feature - Option to enable content restrictions for admin user for testing purposes
* Feature - Added support for automatic updates
* Fix - Limitation of member export tool
* Tweak - Improved language file loading - now also looks in WP_LANG_DIR
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

