Version 2.0, 2 June 2015
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Feature - Conditionally restrict access to URLs with wildcard support
* Feature - New shortcodes and user functions to display membership information
* Feature - Option to send membership expiration reminders at predefined intervals
* Fix - Not possible to remove linked plan
* Fix - Problem related to linked products when product type is changed
* Tweak - Improved members list on plan's page: added pagination and search
* Tweak - Improved compatibility with The Events Calendar and Sensei plugins
* Tweak - Improved member purchases handling within one plan
* Tweak - Improved the way product and member counts are retrieved for membership plans
* Tweak - Small changes related to functionality on demo site
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

Version 1.2, 25 February 2015
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Feature - Method that redirects users to custom URL when post is restricted
* Feature - Export To CSV functionality to export members of specific plan
* Feature - Method to change membership expiration date from plan page
* Feature - Option to restrict access to WooCommerce products
* Feature - Option to make WooCommerce products not purchasable by non-members
* Feature - Added Settings page under Membership menu
* Fix - Bug that allowed access to restricted content when no plan was selected
* Tweak - Optimized loading of admin area assets
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

