Version 1.1.2, 22 December 2014
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Tweak - Support for inner shortcodes
* Tweak - Users with role "administrator" can now view shortcode content by default

Version 1.1.1, 17 December 2014
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Fix - Bug related to membership plan key existence checks
