Version 1.1, 11 September 2014
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Feature - Option to expire memberships after a pre-defined amount of time
* Feature - New post/page access restriction options to cover more scenarios
* Feature - Membership Granted and Membership Expired emails
* Feature - Function that detects duplicate websites to suppress customer emails
* Feature - Option to add/remove members to/from a membership plan manually
* Feature - Support for WooCommerce Dynamic Pricing & Discounts Extension
* Feature - Linked plans feature that allow content drip feed functionality
* Feature - Bulk post edit capabilities
* Tweak - Other minor bug fixes and improvements

Version 1.0.1, 1 September 2014
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Feature - Functions to restrict access to content from within templates
* Fix - Fixed "Can't use method return value in write context" bug in older PHP versions
* Tweak - Improved actions and filters available in this plugin
* Tweak - Improved function that determines system's time zone

